These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-1::.
There 2 different types of food: pumpkin, corn
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, train
1. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the train##1
2. the person eating pumpkin is not to the right of the person driving the train##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |
| Food        | pumpkin   | corn   |
| Transport   | train | boat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is badminton is not to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##8
2. the person who's sport is badminton is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | milk   |
| Sport      | skateboarding | badminton |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-3::.
There 2 different types of food: grapes, zucchini
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: reggae, gospel
1. the person eating grapes is not to the left of the fan of gospel##8
2. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the fan of gospel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Food          | zucchini | grapes |
| Music-Genre   | reggae   | gospel     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-4::.
